{"pageProps":{"bookInfo":{"id":"10045","name":"摘抄","fullPath":"F:\\passerby\\article\\摘抄","chapterList":[{"id":"10045_100000","type":"chapter","name":"摘抄","fullPath":"F:\\passerby\\article\\摘抄\\摘抄.md","url":"/chapter/10045_100000","content":"\n    \n    \n      <div class=\"crossnote markdown-preview  \">\n      \n<h1 id=\"摘抄\">摘抄 </h1>\n<p><strong>《摸鱼儿·雁丘词》-<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%85%83%E5%A5%BD%E9%97%AE?fromModule=lemma_search-box\">元好问</a></strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>问世间，情为何物？直教生死相许。天南地北双飞客，老翅几回寒暑。欢乐趣，离别苦，就中更有痴儿女。君应有语，渺万里层云，千山暮雪，只影向谁去？<br>\n横汾路，寂寞当年箫鼓。荒烟依旧平楚。招魂楚些何嗟及，山鬼暗啼风雨。天也妒，未信与，莺儿燕子俱黄土。千秋万古，为留待骚人，狂歌痛饮，来访雁丘处。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>《墙头马上》 -- <a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%99%BD%E6%9C%B4/556573?fromModule=lemma_inlink\">白朴</a></strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>\"为谁含笑在墙头？莫负后园今夜约\"</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>《庄子 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo>⋅</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\cdot</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4445em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">⋅</span></span></span></span> 齐物论》</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>天地与我并生，而万物与我为一</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>《韩非子 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo>⋅</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\cdot</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4445em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">⋅</span></span></span></span> 大体》</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>寄治乱于 法术，托是非于赏罚，属轻重于权衡</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>《道德经》</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>有物混成，先天地生。寂兮寥兮，独立而不改，周行而不殆，可以为天下母，吾不知其名。 强字之曰道</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>道生一，一生二，二生三，三生万物。万物负阴而抱阳，冲气以为和。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>道大，天大，地大，人亦大。域中有四大，而人居其一焉。人法地，地法天，天法道，道法自然。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>天之道，其犹张弓与？高者抑下，下者举之，有余者损之，不足者补之。天之道，损有余而补不足。人之道，则不然，损不足以奉有余。孰能有余以奉天下，唯有道者。是以圣人为而不恃，功成而不处，其不欲见贤</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>而立不惑知天命，花甲古稀加总年</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>而立 + 不惑 + 知天命 + 花甲 + 古稀 = 30 + 40 + 50 + 60 + 70 = 250</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"md-sidebar-toc\">\n<div class=\"md-toc\">\n<div class=\"md-toc-link-wrapper\" style=\"padding:0;;display:list-item;list-style:square;margin-left:18px\">\n          <a href=\"#摘抄\" class=\"md-toc-link\">\n            <p>摘抄</p>\n\n          </a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n      <a id=\"sidebar-toc-btn\">≡</a>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n<script>\n\nvar sidebarTOCBtn = document.getElementById('sidebar-toc-btn')\nsidebarTOCBtn.addEventListener('click', function(event) {\n  event.stopPropagation()\n  if (document.body.hasAttribute('html-show-sidebar-toc')) {\n    document.body.removeAttribute('html-show-sidebar-toc')\n  } else {\n    document.body.setAttribute('html-show-sidebar-toc', true)\n  }\n})\n</script>\n      \n  \n    "}],"type":"book","url":"/book/10045"},"chapterInfo":{"id":"10045_100000","type":"chapter","name":"摘抄","fullPath":"F:\\passerby\\article\\摘抄\\摘抄.md","url":"/chapter/10045_100000","content":"\n    \n    \n      <div class=\"crossnote markdown-preview  \">\n      \n<h1 id=\"摘抄\">摘抄 </h1>\n<p><strong>《摸鱼儿·雁丘词》-<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%85%83%E5%A5%BD%E9%97%AE?fromModule=lemma_search-box\">元好问</a></strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>问世间，情为何物？直教生死相许。天南地北双飞客，老翅几回寒暑。欢乐趣，离别苦，就中更有痴儿女。君应有语，渺万里层云，千山暮雪，只影向谁去？<br>\n横汾路，寂寞当年箫鼓。荒烟依旧平楚。招魂楚些何嗟及，山鬼暗啼风雨。天也妒，未信与，莺儿燕子俱黄土。千秋万古，为留待骚人，狂歌痛饮，来访雁丘处。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>《墙头马上》 -- <a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%99%BD%E6%9C%B4/556573?fromModule=lemma_inlink\">白朴</a></strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>\"为谁含笑在墙头？莫负后园今夜约\"</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>《庄子 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml